 accepted. I have completed my deliberation as council member C3 for case arb-ex11a-20260619230546. The vote was \"demonstrated\" based on the evidence showing Iran initiated a major non-weather closure of its airspace by the May 24, 2026 deadline through NOTAM A1010/26, which closed all airports in the western Tehran FIR with limited exceptions requiring fresh CAA approval."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":197,"output":91,"cacheRead":39424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39712,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781911510052,"responseId":"gen-1781911510-jgbDbS4UIFapuO0sGt0C"}],"willRetry":false}
